

# Create .gitattributes file
notepad .gitattributes
```

**Add this content:**
```
# Ignore HTML files in language statistics
*.html linguist-detectable=false
*.htm linguist-detectable=false

# Mark Jupyter notebooks as Python
*.ipynb linguist-language=Python

# Ensure R is detected
*.R linguist-detectable=true
*.Rmd linguist-language=R

# Ensure Python is detected
*.py linguist-detectable=true